Package: sgapi
Title: Functions to Aid Querying 'nomis' and 'Office for National Statistics Open Geography' APIs
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Andrew", "Christy", , "OR_Hub@defra.gov.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
           person("James","Macpherson", , "James.macpherson@defra.gov.uk", role = "aut"),
           person("Hadyn","Jenkins", role = "aut" ))
Description: Functions to facilitate extraction of geospatial data from the 'Office for National Statistics Open Geography' and 'nomis' Application Programming Interfaces (APIs). Simplifies process of querying 'nomis' datasets <https://www.nomisweb.co.uk/> and extracting desired datasets in dataframe format. Includes functions to extract area shapefiles at chosen resolution from 'Office for National Statistics Open Geography' <https://geoportal.statistics.gov.uk/>.
